title: HW0 - Palmer Penguin Dataset Visualization
text:
The Palmer Penguin dataset contains data for 344 penguins, including 3 species from 3 different islands in the Palmer Archipelago, Antarctica.
To visualize this data in an interesting manner I decided to graph the penguins’ mass on the x-axis and their flipper length on the y-axis. I then created a scatter plot and seperated the penguins into two groups based on their sex (Male and Female). I then proceeded to add the line of best fit for each group.
